  "text": "The CSS style change propagation through Blink follows this pipeline: (1) **StyleResolver** (`third_party/blink/renderer/core/css/resolver/style_resolver.cc`, class declared at style_resolver.h:63) resolves computed styles for DOM elements \u2014 it's a `GarbageCollected` final class. (2) **LayoutObject** (`third_party/blink/renderer/core/layout/layout_object.cc`, class declared at layout_object.h:270) is the base class for all layout tree nodes (`CORE_EXPORT LayoutObject : public GarbageCollected<LayoutObject>`). (3) **PaintLayer** (`third_party/blink/renderer/core/paint/paint_layer.cc`, class declared at paint_layer.h:174) is the painting layer abstraction (`CORE_EXPORT PaintLayer : public GarbageCollected<PaintLayer>`). (4) For the display list / paint recording stage, there are two key files: **PaintController** (`third_party/blink/renderer/platform/graphics/paint/paint_controller.cc`, class at paint_controller.h:131, `PLATFORM_EXPORT PaintController`) orchestrates paint recording, and **DisplayItemList** (`third_party/blink/renderer/platform/graphics/paint/display_item_list.cc`, class at display_item_list.h:28, `PLATFORM_EXPORT DisplayItemList`) stores the recorded display items. Note that PaintController and DisplayItemList live under `platform/graphics/paint/` rather than `core/paint/`.",
